gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838b109d4baaec0ea79b741a8d710ad1b3b72475","tid":566711,"uid":38539,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"13ce801f810259909be0fab8708cd25aed8c7121","tid":566711,"uid":37197,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:12:28.000Z","msg":"新聞無講點解11歲月致全家中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"香港中毒諮詢中心資料顯示，一名11歲女童去年為一家四口烹調「洋葱炒牛肉」時，誤將放在雪櫃的「水仙頭」當洋葱炒，因水仙頭含有毒生物鹼，一家四口進食後嘔吐及肚瀉。專家建議市民不要將水仙頭放在雪櫃。<br />\n<br />\n劉稱涉事11歲女童烹調「洋葱炒牛肉」，打開雪櫃時不慎將水仙頭誤以為是洋葱，取用切開用以炒牛肉，她與父母及9歲妹妹進食時感味道苦澀，服食後約15至30分鐘，4人相繼肚痛及屙嘔，到急症室求醫，但情况不算嚴重，治療後同日出院。"},{"pid":"b036da997af798c62d675285cb2768d8a87dd5b0","tid":566711,"uid":33864,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"我尋日先飲完水仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97256d4bc23929a49cca3e7ff93f65381e00fbc","tid":566711,"uid":53672,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"屌你無洋葱陣味都醒水啦，仲當無事照食真係豬西到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9ef975c97397ce3696be8a83350494e1f09699","tid":566711,"uid":117577,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns1403041393870359976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns1403041393870359976&d=O5GDw088ZA10p07MbgUQicmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=41575b07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns1403041393870359976&h=0a128322\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpa